headline: Otis Second Quarter 2025 Earnings Advisory
summary: Otis Worldwide Corporation (NYSE: OTIS) will host a conference call on Wednesday, July 23, 2025, at 8:30 a.m. ET. Otis Chair, CEO & President Judy Marks and Executive Vice President & CFO Cristina Mendez will discuss the company's second quarter results and 2025 outlook.
